data.description: Nestled amidst tranquility, this exquisite home offers a serene retreat with a captivating koi pond & 12 magnificent koi fish that convey with the property. Enjoy the seamless flow of living in this turnkey haven, where beauty abounds both inside and out. Step into a spacious open floor plan with 10-foot ceilings. The main bedroom wing offers a secluded sanctuary. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring expansive granite countertops, a pantry, under-cabinet lighting, and a stylish high backsplash, complete with a convenient coffee bar. With 3 bedrooms, an office/den, and 2.5 bathrooms, there's room for all your lifestyle needs. The family room showcases new flooring. A three-car garage, along with an oversized separate single-car garage equipped with HVAC. Outside, a spacious covered patio overlooks the meticulously landscaped yard, boasting xeriscaping and two generous 8'x12' tuff sheds on a corner lot. Welcome to your sanctuary of comfort and style!
